weather-monitoring-app/
│
├── src/
│   ├── config/
│   │   └── settings.py           # Configurable parameters like API Key, cities, and intervals
│   ├── utils/
│   │   └── weather_api.py        # Fetches data from OpenWeatherMap
│   └── main.py                   # Main script for executing the application
│
├── tests/
│   ├── test_weather.py           # Unit and integration tests
│
├── visualizations/
│   └── plots.py                  # Visualize data (matplotlib/plotly)
│
├── requirements.txt              # Dependencies
├── Dockerfile                    # Dockerfile for the project setup
├── docker-compose.yml            # For managing containers like database, webserver
└── README.md                     # Detailed instructions and project overview
